{"questionId":"9076642","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>The table shows the speed of ultrasound and the acoustic impedance for different media.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"https://ib-questionbank-attachments.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/tinymce_asset/asset/4813/Schermafbeelding_2018-08-13_om_15.56.54.png\" alt=\"M18/4/PHYSI/HP3/ENG/TZ1/14.d\"></p>\n<p>The fraction F of the intensity of an ultrasound wave reflected at the boundary between two media having acoustic impedances Z<sub>1</sub> and Z<sub>2</sub> is given by F =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{{{({{\\text{Z}}_1} - {{\\text{Z}}_2})}^2}}}{{{{({{\\text{Z}}_1} + {{\\text{Z}}_2})}^2}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n            <mrow>\n              <msub>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mtext>Z</mtext>\n                </mrow>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n              </msub>\n            </mrow>\n            <mo>−</mo>\n            <mrow>\n              <msub>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mtext>Z</mtext>\n                </mrow>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </msub>\n            </mrow>\n            <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo>\n            <mrow>\n              <msub>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mtext>Z</mtext>\n                </mrow>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n              </msub>\n            </mrow>\n            <mo>+</mo>\n            <mrow>\n              <msub>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mtext>Z</mtext>\n                </mrow>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </msub>\n            </mrow>\n            <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Calculate the density of skin.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><em>ρ</em> =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{1.99 \\times {{10}^6}}}{{1.73 \\times {{10}^3}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1.99</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>6</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>1.73</mn>\n      <mo>×</mo>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n          </mrow>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> = 1.15&nbsp;× 10<sup>3</sup>&nbsp;<strong>«</strong>kgm<sup>–3</sup><strong>»</strong></p>\n<p><em><strong>[1 mark]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9076642","referenceCode":"18M.3.HL.TZ1.d.i","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"Calculate the density of skin.","paper":"3","level":"HL","questionNumber":"d.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Option C: Imaging","Option C: Imaging","Option C: Imaging (Additional higher level option topics)","C.4 – Medical imaging (HL only)","Option C: Imaging","Option C: Imaging (Additional higher level option topics)"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}